title: [Solhaven, Spiral Passageway]
description: Faded silk banners with their words long gone hang in frayed valances, draping from each oil  mounted on the passageway walls.  The end of one section hangs down limply, detached from the remainder and trailing in a rivulet of water meandering along the cobblestones.
